description: Lists the data set imports for the specified application.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the application.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the data set import task.

nested_items.name: statusReason
nested_items.description: If dataset import failed, the failure reason will show here.

nested_items.name: failed
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that have failed.

nested_items.name: inProgress
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that are in progress.

nested_items.name: pending
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that are pending.

nested_items.name: succeeded
nested_items.description: The number of data set imports that have succeeded.

nested_items.name: total
nested_items.description: The total number of data set imports.

nested_items.name: taskId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the data set import task.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more items to return, this contains a token that is passed to a subsequent call to this operation to retrieve the next set of items.
